{"word":"ἠμέν","slug":"ἠμέν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46965\" key=\"h)me/n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἠμέν</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Conj., correl. to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἠδέ</foreign> (from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἦ</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μέν, δέ</foreign>), <sense id=\"n46965.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">both . . </tr_> and . . , <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. νέοι ἠδὲ γέροντες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:789\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.789</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. ἀνακλῖναι πυκινὸν νέφος ἠδ᾽ ἐπιθεῖναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:751\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.751</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; sts. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καί</foreign> is added to <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠδέ, ἠ. θεὸν ἠδὲ καὶ ἄνδρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:128\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.128</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. δέμας ἠδὲ καὶ αὐδήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:268\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.268</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. δή ποτ᾽ ἐμεῦ πάρος ἔκλυες . . ἠδ᾽ ἔτι καὶ νῦν μοι . . ἐπικρήηνον ἐέλδωρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:453\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.453</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: rarely folld. by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δέ</foreign> or <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">τε</itype><cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, ἠ . . . πολλοὶ δέ . . </quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:428\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.428</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. ὅσοι χαλεποί . . οἵ τε φιλόξεινοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:575\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.575</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: more freq. by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καί</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:664\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.664</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:670\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">670</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:339\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">339</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}